		{
			"name": "Purchase Headers",
			"description": "Purchase order workflow:\n1. **Create** → status is `draft`\n2. **Add items** via nested `/purchase-headers/{purchase}/items`\n3. **Complete** → creates inventory records + stock movements, status becomes `completed`\n4. **Completed purchases are immutable** — no edits, no cancellation\n5. **Cancel** only works for **draft** purchases\n\n**Error responses for business rule violations (HTTP 400):**\n```json\n{\n    \"success\": false,\n    \"status\": 400,\n    \"message\": \"Only draft purchases can be completed.\",\n    \"errors\": null\n}\n```",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "List Purchase Headers",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/purchase-headers",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["purchase-headers"],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "per_page",
									"value": "10"
								}
							]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Create Purchase Header",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"supplier_id\": 1,\n  \"notes\": \"Monthly stock order\",\n  \"supplier_invoice_number\": \"INV-2024-001\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/purchase-headers",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["purchase-headers"]
						}
					},
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('purchase_id', jsonData.data.id);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Get Purchase Header",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/purchase-headers/{{purchase_id}}",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["purchase-headers", "{{purchase_id}}"]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Update Purchase Header",
					"description": "**Immutability rule:** Only draft purchases can be updated.\n- The `status` field is **not allowed** in the request body.\n- Status can only be changed via `Complete` or `Cancel` endpoints.\n\n**Error response if completed/cancelled:**\n```json\n{\n    \"success\": false,\n    \"status\": 400,\n    \"message\": \"لا يمكن تعديل فاتورة مكتملة أو ملغاة.\",\n    \"errors\": null\n}\n```",
					"request": {
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"supplier_id\": 1,\n  \"notes\": \"Updated notes\",\n  \"supplier_invoice_number\": \"INV-2024-002\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/purchase-headers/{{purchase_id}}",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["purchase-headers", "{{purchase_id}}"]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Delete Purchase Header",
					"description": "**Immutability rule:** Only draft purchases can be deleted.",
					"request": {
						"method": "DELETE",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/purchase-headers/{{purchase_id}}",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["purchase-headers", "{{purchase_id}}"]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Complete Purchase Header",
